kasi yathirai ( தமிழ் : காசியாத்திரை , english : pilgrimage to kasi ( or ) journey to kasi ) is a 1973 tamil language comedy film directed by s. p. muthuraman and produced by s. s. sethuraman under sri devi cine tone . the film 's script was written by v. c. guhanathan . soundtrack was composed by shankar ganesh . the film stars v. k. ramasamy , sreekanth , suruli rajan in lead roles with kumari padmini , jaya , manorama ( played dual role in the film one is stage-drama actress andal and another is dr. dhamodran daughter lalitha ) , m. r. r. vasu and cho ramaswamy portraying supporting role . kamal haasan worked under thangappan as his dance assistant in this movie .